{
  "stem": "9102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, we saw-- you know, I've seen enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because those people when they were put on the transportation, they didn't-- well, it was all kind of ages, of course, young people, older people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if they didn't move fast enough, they just did the, you know, just [INAUDIBLE] hit them and all this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've seen some people being shot, being trying to escape from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But, you know, I guess you were young and you didn't really-- well, of course, you knew it was, you know, what it was and could happen to anybody.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you know, if we had been picked up, if we hadn't been hidden in that place we would have been picked up that night, too.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There must have been, there was, you know, quite an active group of the underground in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they also, the underground, that section of the underground what took care of me also, uh, got rid of quite-- got hold of quite a few of the smaller babies from the assembly hall where all the people were put down.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, one of the nurses in there helped to get them escaped right across the street from where they were brought over.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because later on, after the war, we found-- you know, heard quite a bit of stories of the Jewish people who had-- who were babies, really, who went from there and were brought also to Limburg, the province of Limburg.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one of the kids also who was hidden in Limburg what turned out to be later on the mayor of Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Van Thijn.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
